**Setup:**
- 10 triples of patients means 30 total patients (10 get drug 1, 10 get drug 2, 10 get drug 3)
- Each drug is given to exactly 10 patients
- Each drug has success probability p = 0.7
- Let X₁, X₂, X₃ be the number of successes for drugs 1, 2, 3 respectively
