= 1 × 0.028247953 × 1
= 0.028247953

P(X ≥ 9) = 0.121060821 + 0.028247953 = 0.149308774

P(X ≤ 8) = 1 - 0.149308774 = 0.850691226

**Computing the final probability:**

P(max ≤ 8) = (0.850691226)³ = 0.614527888

P(max > 8) = 1 - 0.614527888 = 0.385472112

